<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q44_v2" title="Q44_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd"><qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"><qti-correct-response><qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value></qti-correct-response></qti-response-declaration><qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body><p>Un estudiante ha rendido ya tres pruebas en un semestre y sabe que su promedio actual es 5,5. Debe rendir una cuarta prueba, cuya nota representamos por <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones permite determinar el promedio final del estudiante en función de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>?</p><qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1"><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>5.5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>16.5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>5.5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></qti-simple-choice><qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD"><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>16.5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></qti-simple-choice></qti-choice-interaction></qti-item-body><qti-response-processing template="https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml" /></qti-assessment-item>